name: Blue Pincushion
description:
+ Fine Art Macro Photography of Scabiosa Butterfly Blue

+ Hand-signed & dated on back

+ Professionally printed on archival lustre professional photo paper 

+ 8 x 10 and 11 x 14 prints will be cropped slightly 

+ 16 x 24 canvas print will have black 1-1/4" depth wraparound edges and come with a backer board and pre-installed handing hardware

+ Be sure to review the Customer Service page to review payment, shipping and return policies

name: 2014 Fine Art Landscape Photography Calendar
description:
+ 12 month calendar featuring original fine art landscape images 

+ Printed on 110 lb. heavy smooth card stock for a modern matte look

+ 14 loose sheets (12 months plus front and back covers) measuring 5x7 inches

+ Images can be cut and framed to 3.5x5 inches when month is over

+ Calendar can be displayed on mini-easel, clipped or hole-punched for hanging

+ Wrapped in hemp twine and packaged in clear sealed envelope - perfect for gifting!

+ Shipped flat in rigid kraft mailer

+ Go to neelywang.com to view additional product images
